(1, 195, NULL, 'EQUIPMENT:RECREATIONAL VEHICLE/TRAILER:LPG SYSTEMS:WATER HEATER ', 29, 'Roadtrek Inc. (Roadtrek) is recalling certain 2021-2022 Zion, Zion SRT, Zion Slumber, Chase, Play, and Play Slumber recreational vehicles. The propane line may not be attached to the water heater.', 'An unattached propane line can cause gas to enter the vehicle, increasing the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will inspect and attach the propane line, as necessary, and test the propane system, free of charge.  Owners may contact Roadtrek customer service at 1-888-762-3873.  Roadtrek\'s number for this recall is 2022-01.'),
