(643, 371, NULL, 'FUEL SYSTEM, GASOLINE:STORAGE:TANK ASSEMBLY:FILLER PIPE AND CAP', 18366, 'Ford Motor Company (Ford) is recalling certain 2022 Explorer and Lincoln Aviator vehicles.  The fuel filler tube may detach during a crash.  As such, these vehicles fail to comply with the requirements of Federal Motor Vehicle Safety Standard number 301, \"Fuel System Integrity.\"', 'A detached fuel filler tube can result in a fuel leak, increasing the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will install a fuel vapor line redundant locking clip, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed on April 4, 2022.  Owners may contact Ford customer service at 1-866-436-7332.  Ford\'s number for this recall is 22C02.'),
