(693, 388, NULL, 'STEERING:HYDRAULIC POWER ASSIST:PUMP', 91, 'Shyft Group is recalling certain 2020-2022 Spartan RV Chassis K3 and K4 recreational vehicles.  A machining defect may cause pressure to build in the power steering pump and break the shaft seal, resulting in a loss of power steering assist.  ', 'A loss of power steering assist increases the risk of a crash.', 'Shyft Group will inspect the pump serial number, and replace the power steering pump if necessary, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed November 23, 2021.  Owners may contact Shyft Group\'s customer service at 1-800-582-3454.  Shyft Group\'s number for this recall is 21-21.  '),
