(811, 433, NULL, 'STEERING:RACK AND PINION', 151, 'Toyota Motor Engineering & Manufacturing (Toyota) is recalling certain JTEKT power steering gear assembly service parts for 2007-2021 Tundra and 2008-2022 Sequoia, part numbers 44250-0C160, 44250-0C131, 44250-0C170, and 11250-0C121.  The power steering gear assembly may have been manufactured incorrectly, which can result in an oil leak. ', 'An oil leak may cause a sudden loss of power steering assist, increasing the risk of a crash. ', 'Dealers will inspect and replace the power steering gear assembly, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed on February 17, 2022.  Owners may contact Toyota customer service at 1-800-331-4331.  Toyota\'s number for this recall is 21TH01. '),
