(986, 442, NULL, 'FUEL SYSTEM, DIESEL:DELIVERY:HOSES, LINES/PIPING, AND FITTINGS', 330, 'Tiffin Motorhomes, Inc. (Tiffin) is recalling certain 2021-2022 Allegro Bus and Phaeton motorhomes, equipped with certain Cummins L9 diesel engines.  A fuel leak may occur from the fuel hose between the fuel pump and remote filter head.', 'A fuel leak in the presence of an ignition source can increase the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will replace the fuel hoses, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed September 10, 2021.  Owners may contact Tiffin customer service at 1-256-356-8661.  Tiffin\'s number for this recall is TIF-117.'),
