(988, 444, NULL, 'TIRES:TREAD/BELT', 2363, 'Heartland Recreational Vehicles, LLC (Heartland) is recalling certain 2021-2022 Cyclone, Fuel, Gravity, and Warrior vehicles equipped with certain Sailun tires, sizes ST235/80R16 and ST235/85R16.  Due to a manufacturing issue, the tires may experience a belt separation. ', 'Belt separation could lead to loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of a crash. ', 'Dealers will inspect the tire DOT codes, and replace the tires as necessary, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed March 7, 2022.  Owners may contact Heartland customer service at 1-877-262-8032 or Sailun customer service at 1-844-281-9696.'),
