(1496, 555, NULL, 'ENGINE AND ENGINE COOLING:ENGINE:GASOLINE:TURBO/SUPERCHARGER', 26, 'Kia Motor America (Kia) is recalling certain 2022 Sorento vehicles.  The oil supply pipe to the turbocharger may crack, which could result in an oil leak in the engine compartment.', 'An oil leak in the presence of an ignition source such as hot engine or exhaust components, can increase the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will replace the turbocharger oil supply pipe, free of charge.  Owner notification letters are expected to be mailed April 22, 2022.  Owners may contact Kia customer service at 1-800-333-4542.  Kia\'s number for this recall is SC233.'),
