(1874, 637, NULL, 'TRAILER HITCHES', 690, 'Big Tex Trailer Manufacturing, Inc. (Big Tex Trailer) is recalling certain 2022 50SR and 70SR trailers.  The coupler was improperly welded, which may cause the trailer to separate from the tow vehicle.', 'Trailer separation from a tow vehicle can increase the risk of a crash. ', 'Dealers will inspect and replace the coupler as necessary, free of charge.  Owner notification letters are expected to be mailed on May 9, 2022.  Owners may contact Big Tex Trailer\'s customer service at 1-800-594-5637. '),
