(1911, 641, NULL, 'ELECTRICAL SYSTEM:WIRING', 84, 'Jayco, Inc. (Jayco) is recalling certain 2022 Alante Class A and Entegra Coach Vision Class A motorhomes.  The main chassis harness may be positioned too close to the exhaust manifold, causing the wiring to melt.', 'A melted wiring harness can cause the vehicle to stall, increasing the risk of a crash.', 'Dealers will inspect and secure the harness as necessary, or replace the harness if damage is found, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed January 6, 2022.  Owners may contact Jayco customer service at 1-800-283-8267.  '),
