(1941, 268, NULL, 'TIRES', 21, 'Forest River, Inc. (Forest River) is recalling certain 2022 Vengeance Fifth Wheel trailers.  The tire pressure label may indicate incorrect tire pressure information for the front tires.  As such, these vehicles fail to comply with the requirements of Federal Motor Vehicle Safety Standard numbers 120, \"Wheels and Rims-Other Than Passenger Cars\" and 567, \"Certification.\" ', 'Incorrect tire pressure information may result in under-inflated tires that can fail, increasing the risk of a crash. ', 'Forest River will mail replacement labels, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed February 8, 2022.  Owners may contact Forest River customer service at 1-260-499-2100.  Forest River\'s number for this recall is 81-1462. '),
