(2035, 413, NULL, 'ELECTRICAL SYSTEM:WIRING:FUSES AND CIRCUIT BREAKERS', 8, 'KZRV, L.P. (KZRV) is recalling certain 2022 Stratus and SportTrek trailers.  The water heater and fireplace circuits were improperly connected to a 20amp circuit breaker instead of a 15amp circuit breaker.', 'The wrong amperage circuit breaker may not provide adequate circuit protection, increasing the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will replace circuit breaker, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed December 6, 2021.  Owners may contact KZRV customer service at 1-800-768-4016 ext. 154 or 153.  KZRV\'s number for this recall is KZ-2021-06.'),
