(2253, 683, NULL, 'EQUIPMENT:APPLIANCE:OVEN/STOVE/COOKTOP', 140, 'StarCraft RV (StarCraft) is recalling certain 2021 Autumn Ridge Outfitter recreational trailers.  The cooktop is installed in a cabinet that may not be entirely sealed from the furnace.  As a result, during furnace operation, the interior range cooktop burner flame may invert.', 'An inverted flame can increase the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will install sealant and plywood panels, as necessary, free of charge.  Owner notification letters were mailed November 29, 2021.  Owners may contact StarCraft customer service at 1-800-283-8267.  StarCraft\'s number for this recall is 9902571.'),
