(2383, 706, NULL, 'ENGINE AND ENGINE COOLING:ENGINE:GASOLINE:TURBO/SUPERCHARGER', 16, 'Hyundai Motor America (Hyundai) is recalling certain 2022 Santa Fe and Santa Cruz vehicles.  The oil supply pipe to the turbocharger may crack, which could result in an oil leak in the engine compartment.', 'An oil leak in the presence of an ignition source such as hot engine or exhaust components, can increase the risk of a fire.', 'Dealers will replace the turbocharger oil supply pipe, free of charge.  Owner notification letters are expected to be mailed May 27, 2022.  Owners may contact Hyundai customer service at 1-855-371-9460.  Hyundai\'s number for this recall 222.  '),
