(2680, 811, NULL, 'PARKING BRAKE', 499, 'Transcraft Corporation (Transcraft) is recalling certain 2016-2021 Platform trailers equipped with certain fork lift kits and adjustable wheel stops.  The adjustable wheel stops may detach.', 'If the wheel stop detaches while the trailer is parked and in use, there is an increased risk of crash or injury.', 'Transcraft notified owners and provided repair instructions to inspect and repair the wheel stop assemblies, free of charge.  The recall began November 13, 2020.  Owners may contact Transcraft customer service at 1-877-489-9020.  Transcraft\'s number for this recall is B20016.'),
