(2687, 812, NULL, 'SUSPENSION:FRONT:SPRINGS:LEAF SPRING ASSEMBLY:U-BOLT, LEAF SPRING TO AXLE', 209, 'Keystone RV Company (Keystone) is recalling certain 2021 Crossroads Redwood 3401RL, 3901MB, 3901WB, 3911RL, 3951MB, 3951WB, 3981FK, 3991RD, 4001LK, 4150RD recreational trailers, built on D80 Dexter Axles.  The U-bolts on these axles may have been improperly torqued, causing the bolts to loosen and the axle to slide.', 'If the axle moves, poor vehicle handling may result, increasing the risk of a crash.', 'Keystone will notify owners, and dealers will properly tighten the U-bolts, free of charge.  The recall began February 8, 2021.  Owners may contact Keystone customer service at 1-866-425-4369.  Keystone\'s number for this recall is 21-394.'),
