(2958, 770, NULL, 'ELECTRICAL SYSTEM:12V/24V/48V BATTERY', 63, 'Thor Motor Coach (TMC) is recalling certain 2021 Daybreak, Four Winds, Quantum, Chateau, and Freedom Elite motorhomes built on the 2020 Ford E-Series chassis.  The battery cable may not have been properly secured within the chassis rail, which can cause it to contact the exhaust manifold and heat shield.', 'Battery cable contact with the exhaust manifold and heat shield can increase the risk of a fire. ', 'TMC will notify owners, and dealers will inspect the routing of the battery cable.  If needed the cable will be re-routed and properly secured, free of charge.  This recall began September 11, 2020.  Owners may contact TMC customer service at 1-877-855-2867.  TMC\'s number for this recall is RC000197.'),
